---
title: Mumbai Potato & Cauliflower Dhal with Garlic Dippers
description: Put that take-away flyer down because we've got something in store for you. Mumbai spices work their magic with hearty lentils and creamy coconut milk in our new favourite dhal recipe. Oven-baked tortilla dippers work a treat for scooping up the deliciousness.

